item.title: On the Osculating Spaces of Submanifolds in Euclidean Spaces
item.description: arXiv:2501.14798v1 Announce Type: new Abstract: This paper is a continuation of the papers [2,3,4,5,6]. In this paper the osculating spaces of arbitrary order of a manifold embedded in Euclidean space are considered. A better estimation of their dimensions as well as the description of its basis are given.
